&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute device testing in accordance with Beacon’s QMS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and document test plans, test protocols, and test scripts for embedded systems, including hardware, firmware, and software, based on design specifications and requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain test procedures, fixtures, and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct functional, integration, system, and regression testing on hardware and firmware.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with hardware and firmware engineers to troubleshoot and resolve product issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure products meet industry standards, safety, and regulatory requirements (e.g., FDA, CE, 60601).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement process improvements and test automation to enhance product quality and testing efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
